cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SY, cs.DM

The paper discusses the functional equivalence between Takagi-Sugeno-Kang fuzzy systems and other machine learning approaches for regression problems. This makes it likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning and artificial intelligence, such as cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also touches upon control systems, which could place it in the sub-category of cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper discusses the curse of dimensionality, which is a common problem in data mining, making cs.DM (Data Mining) another possible sub-category.
